{"tid":2308553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（耐人尋味）警方拘捕一名39歲男子 涉冒充警員訂購飲料但未有付款","createTime":"2020-12-02T03:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T04:39:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fb99d778b696bbc4c8faaa8a097f923d5d2d92fe","tid":2308553,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:28:34.000Z","msg":"警方昨晚拘捕一名39歲男子，涉嫌在去年冒充警員，向一間飲品代理訂購大批飲品送往多間警署，但未有付款，被警方以冒警及以欺詐手段取得財產拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n　警方表示，荃灣一間飲品代理公司，去年8月收到一名男子電話，報稱是警員並訂購共340箱飲品，要求公司送往多間警署。飲品公司送貨後，各間警署都有警員接收，而代理公司想向訂購飲品的男子收款時，男子以不同藉口推搪，最終沒有付款。飲品公司今日報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n　警方調查後，相信有人向被捕的騙徒捐款，吩咐騙徒訂購飲品送往警署，但騙徒訂購完侵吞了款項，未有向飲品公司付清賬項。<br />\n<br />\n　警方提醒，冒充警務人員及以欺騙手段取得財產為嚴重罪行。一經定罪，最高可被監禁10年，呼籲大家請勿以身試法。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.hkcd .com/content/2020-12/02/content_1232993.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"4bcff0c7838f5a43e5666daebe50a61801672d32","tid":2308553,"uid":3241,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:29:41.000Z","msg":"廢藍互相食夾棍"},{"pid":"733f10d8d20b2ac6552157adb4edc797ea6239fc","tid":2308553,"uid":321046,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:30:59.000Z","msg":"飲品去左邊？憑空消失？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAsir pay俾錢？"},{"pid":"7b8d965dc20a8122ffe887d9e6f07f9e3f2c6f5a","tid":2308553,"uid":35712,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:34:06.000Z","msg":"咁d 差佬又會飲d 野飲 係咪識架"},{"pid":"fdfc1b4272a99af3872a7f2d522e9dd8ff071062","tid":2308553,"uid":32721,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:34:30.000Z","msg":"好信唔信信藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49641c643f36ae72a8ea2146c89782dbf61d2dec","tid":2308553,"uid":40867,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:36:10.000Z","msg":"飲品公司送貨後，各間警署都有警員接收<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇訂過你學人收？<br />\n死黑警自己填數啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee1d871849bdda381446eb44bfc19b098a0351c","tid":2308553,"uid":3860,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:36:51.000Z","msg":"光明正大接賊贓都得，黑警又創犯罪紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f03fbeb5d1e9599ec1492cfe1f5d07d551d404b","tid":2308553,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fdfc1b4272a99af3872a7f2d522e9dd8ff071062","tid":2308553,"uid":32721,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:34:30.000Z","msg":"好信唔信信藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:37:12.000Z","msg":"有心呃捐款既就收左錢走佬啦<br />\n仲真係去訂嘢飲再走數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88dfe14ab9072eef46e2cd6e2aabd08beae898b4","tid":2308553,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://christiantimes.org.hk/News/159978/IMG_2864.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchristiantimes.org.hk%2FNews%2F159978%2FIMG_2864.jpg&h=32604931&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"255ad158b7e7ca579d773b861670adbe59352fb6","tid":2308553,"uid":3860,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0ee1d871849bdda381446eb44bfc19b098a0351c","tid":2308553,"uid":3860,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:36:51.000Z","msg":"光明正大接賊贓都得，黑警又創犯罪紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:38:30.000Z","msg":"補充<br />\n<br />\n根據《盜竊罪條例》，任何人如知道或相信某些貨品是贓物，而不誠實地收受該貨品，或不誠實地從事或協助另一人或為另一人的利益而將該貨品保留、搬遷、處置或變現，即干犯俗稱「接贓」的處理贓物罪，一經定罪最高可判監禁14年。"},{"pid":"ad9e5e6da5b8c56d21c64e80eaa316b20bc278c7","tid":2308553,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:39:00.000Z","msg":"係咪搵第三者訂就可以食霸王餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e726fa60b524ed9331de82dac759950b1a100f4","tid"